content: I've eaten a whole foods, plant based diet for a week... and I don't crave coffee anymore.  WHAT IS GOING ON???? https://t.co/gbX0yxSzKN
I want a minimally processed, whole foods, plant based, low oil, low salt, high flavor meal that I can nuke in 30 seconds... is this too much to ask???

So I'm trying a whole foods, plant based diet for two months...  wish me luck bc I love steak, shrimp, crabs, eggs, bacon, and cheese.  If you know any solid alternatives (that I can get in ND,) let me know. https://t.co/bdjuzKsiOz
